{"tid":449893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【加泰獨立】中國網民力撐：民主自由的勝利","createTime":"2017-10-27T15:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T15:58:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2daa6c9f514a3e963f57d153e1e816df6c157a73","tid":449893,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171024/20192598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F20192598&d=UxoTh%2BK7Wvm%2F5dIuiJw1O2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a770a107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F20192598&h=e5ca78e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171024/20192598</a><br />\n<br />\n 【加泰獨立】中國網民力撐：民主自由的勝利<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1027 22:14<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 加泰羅利亞宣佈脫離西班牙獨立的消息，內地媒體都有簡短的報道，而且消息也在社交媒體上廣傳，不少網民稱「報道越短，事情越大，都稱他們正在「見證歷史」，大讚這是「這是民主的勝利，自由的勝利」，甚至稱「人權大於主權」，不過，網民都擔心加泰沒有其他強國的支持，獨立的路可能十分難走。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n好大壹張弓：這是民主的勝利，自由的勝利！<br />\n<br />\n知吃識：人權大於主權！<br />\n<br />\n李成東：民主大法好！<br />\n<br />\n李儒：又見證歷史性時刻了！<br />\n<br />\n地上霜8888：大一統的結果&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n小米核潛艇：早分早好！別利用政策打着國家的名義，把其他地方吸乾再來建個烏托邦。<br />\n<br />\nFriDayso：請問這對中國有甚麼影響嗎？<br />\n<br />\n勞記有爾R：國足排名又下降一位了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n新新微博"},{"pid":"135518ba2fec7c16ba7df5d4b65435d7cb27d117","tid":449893,"uid":3454,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"勞記有爾R：國足排名又下降一位了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00910a5c77ce015ff20079f1993b107da9a7518b","tid":449893,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勞記有爾R：國足排名又下降一位了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<b